Cell["\<\
For an operator with non-zero spin, the last flavor index should be \
consistent with the proper spin component. In the example below, the flavor \
index was not consistent and hence the spin is regarded as zero:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1964327617,ExpressionUUID->"a6907f82-7eca-4eba-9c01-65a815cfeaa7"],

